information: The company MEPRO DR. JAEGER U. BERGMANN GMBH, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1976, which operates in the Cereals and grains industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans, Fish, Flour and semolina, and Feeds for animal farming industries. It is based in Vechta, Germany.
